Title: Designates that portion of interstate eighty-four that lies within the county of Putnam as the "Putnam County Purple Heart Highway"
Summary: Designates that portion of interstate eighty-four that lies within the county of Putnam as the "Putnam County Purple Heart Highway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system in Putnam county as the "Putnam County Purple Heart Highway"
